Phase 3 readme

## How to Run

1. Start Apache:
sudo service apache2 start

2. Make sure files are in CGI:
sudo cp webpages/.py /usr/lib/cgi-bin/
sudo chmod +x /usr/lib/cgi-bin/.py

3. Open in browser:
http://localhost/cgi-bin/faculty.py  
http://localhost/cgi-bin/courses.py  

---

## Database Setup

Open PostgreSQL:
sudo -u postgres psql

Connect:
\c dashboard

Check tables:
\dt

View data:
SELECT * FROM faculty;
SELECT * FROM courses;

---

